     H            Y.
     F** AKBR13 ****************************************
     F* .. KANBAN NUMBER ADJUST LIST                   *               ST.. *
     F*    MSK KUNIEDA                2000.07.13       *
     F**************************************** AKBR13 **
     FAKBWP13 IP  F     100            DISK
     FAKBPR13 O   E             55     PRINTER
     IAKBWP13 AA
     I                                        1   1 IKUBN L1
     I                                        2   6 ISHN1
     I                                        7  11 ISHN2
     I                                       12  13 ISHN3
     I                                       14  14 ITKR1
     I                                       15  16 ITKR2
     I                                       17  18 ITKR3
     I                                       19  19 ITKR4
     I                                       20  220IKALL
     I                                       23  250IKMIN
     I                                       26  280IKMAX
     I                                       29  310ISRMS
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  14 @HIN
     I                                        1   5 @SHN1
     I                                        6   6 WKF1
     I                                        7  11 @SHN2
     I                                       12  12 WKF2
     I                                       13  14 @SHN3
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   9 @TKR
     I                                        1   1 @TKR1
     I                                        2   2 WKF3
     I                                        3   4 @TKR2
     I                                        5   5 WKF4
     I                                        6   7 @TKR3
     I                                        8   8 WKF5
     I                                        9   9 @TKR4
      *--------------------*
      * INITAL PROCESS     *
      *--------------------*
     C           PSW       IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     TIME           @TIME
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     @DATE
     C                     MOVE '1'       PSW     1
     C                     WRITEAKBPR131
     C                     WRITEAKBPR132
     C                     END
      *--------------------*
      * DETAIL PROCESS     *
      *--------------------*
     C                     ADD  1         @RECD   40
      *
     C                     MOVE ISHN1     @SHN1
     C                     MOVE '-'       WKF1
     C                     MOVE ISHN2     @SHN2
     C                     MOVE '-'       WKF2
     C                     MOVE ISHN3     @SHN3
     C           ISHN3     IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    WKF2
     C                     END
      *
     C                     MOVE ITKR1     @TKR1
     C                     MOVE '-'       WKF3
     C                     MOVE ITKR2     @TKR2
     C                     MOVE '-'       WKF4
     C                     MOVE ITKR3     @TKR3
     C                     MOVE '-'       WKF5
     C                     MOVE ITKR4     @TKR4
     C                     Z-ADDIKALL     @KALL
     C                     Z-ADDIKMIN     @KMIN
     C                     Z-ADDIKMAX     @KMAX
     C                     Z-ADDISRMS     @SRMS
      *
     C                     WRITEAKBPR133
     C           *IN55     IFEQ '1'
     C                     WRITEAKBPR131
     C                     WRITEAKBPR132
     C                     SETOF                       55
     C                     END
     CL1                   WRITEAKBPR134
     CL1                   Z-ADD0         @RECD
